text: Baras may refer to: * Baras (Sophene), a town of ancient Sophene, in Mesopotamia * Baras, Catanduanes, a municipality in the Philippines * Baras, Rizal, a municipality in the Philippines * Baras, Indonesia, a subdistrict in Pasangkayu Regency, West Sulawesi * Baras (TV Lithuania) a Lithuanian reality television program, based on The Bar Swedish reality competition television franchise ==See also== *Barras (disambiguation) *Barrass
